text: ( Source : US Senate Committee on Judiciary ) Monday, October 19 , 2015 U.S. Sen. David Vitter (R-La.) spoke on the floor of the U.S. Senate ahead of a vote tomorrow on his legislation, the Stop Sanctuary Policies and Protect Americans Act ,
